Model bootstrapping

model_bootstrap.lm.Rd

Model bootstrapping

# S3 method for lm
model_bootstrap(model, iterations = 1000, silent = FALSE,
  ...)

# S3 method for merMod
model_bootstrap(model, iterations = 1000,
  silent = FALSE, ...)

Arguments

model

Statistical model.
iterations

The number of bootstrap replicates.
silent

Hide possible refit messages.
...

Arguments passed to or from other methods.

Examples

model <- lm(mpg ~ wt + cyl, data = mtcars)
model_bootstrap(model)
